description: The Jibarito Stop is bringing the streets of Chicago amazing and affordable Puerto Rican classics! Start out with one of several types of empanadas, fritters, or plantains, and pair it with one of their classic Puerto Rican plates. The Jibarito Stop's Pernil (Roasted Pork)Bistec Encebollado (Steak cooked with Peppers and Onions) and Pollo Encebollado (Chicken and peppers are all authentic and mouth watering. End your experience with therir incredible carmel flan.
name: The Jibarito Stop
